Alias My_D+   D+
Alias My_D-   D-

ChargeConj My_D- My_D+

Decay My_D-
  1.0 K+ pi- pi- D_DALITZ;
Enddecay
CDecay My_D+

Decay B+sig
  1.0 My_D+ pi+ My_D- FLATSQDALITZ;
Enddecay
CDecay B-sig

End
